{"tid":1846311,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"醫護罷工戰線要市民支持！！！","createTime":"2020-01-27T14:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T15:02:54.000Z","uid":212944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4be949c63005550d0df170a92f8939662a2a33","tid":1846311,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbfJjzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbfJjzm.jpg&h=3292c325&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n非常感謝各界對醫護的支持。<br />\n我哋明白大家都好著急，我哋比大家一樣更加著急。<br />\n政府每遲一分行動，我哋就要承受多一分風險。<br />\n<br />\n我哋知道病毒唔等人，亦知道件事係幾咁刻不容緩。<br />\n我哋唔明白點解有能力做嘢嘅政府到呢個關頭仍然踢都唔郁。<br />\n到今日仍然連最基本嘅戴口罩都唔願意叫大家戴，到今日仍然覺得事情未嚴重到需要倒截源頭。<br />\n唔通等到一發不可收拾先做嘢。<br />\n<br />\n我哋恨自己不能做得更多，也恨不能更快。<br />\n因為我哋係法定組織，我哋行動有法律限制。<br />\n我哋嘅行動都必須要通過會員大會得到授權，先有能力進行合法嘅工業行動，參與嘅會員先會受到保障。而會員大會又需要通知時限，呢啲係我哋嘅無奈，亦無能為力嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n醫護罷工從來不容易，我哋負擔既係人命。<br />\n我哋面對嘅係前所未有嘅兩難局面。<br />\n咁多年嚟我哋就算環境再艱難仍默默承受，我哋幾乎未有過任何工業行動。即使前段時間颱風襲港，颶風底下我哋仍然冒險上班。<br />\n但今次面對政府嘅不作為，我哋唔可以再沉默。<br />\n呢個決定對大多數同事嚟講係艱難嘅，同為前線承受嘅壓力同心理關口有幾大我哋心中有數。<br />\n更唔好提濃厚嘅白色恐怖氣氛同秋後算帳嘅風險。<br />\n<br />\n冇人希望我哋要走最後一步。如果政府仍不願意多走一步的話，請各位為自己為同事為大眾，站起來一次。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持罷工聯署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/R6Hgvv3TCHwbqXWJ9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FR6Hgvv3TCHwbqXWJ9&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=5d89b67a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/R6Hgvv3TCHwbqXWJ9</a><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/photos/a.116961523108322/135192017951939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHA.EmployAlliance%2Fphotos%2Fa.116961523108322%2F135192017951939&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=b8036673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/photos/a.116961523108322/135192017951939</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">快啲簽啦！！！</span>"},{"pid":"4d5b827986b2ffaeae73fcaaf650a284b707fc31","tid":1846311,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"我支持醫護罷工！"},{"pid":"cf7b5d0be9aa298959b20482317feac5eaef215a","tid":1846311,"uid":111720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"旺角有藍絲被𠝹頸私了昏迷倒地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844228</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec3eb79978360e3adceb7c1be52c4d3e324a89b9","tid":1846311,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:36:22.000Z","msg":"得返一日時間 一句講晒  1.29罷工加黎明行動 做定唔做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846030</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b3ae9c4df3d05c5552f96774c5093098a4cd27a8","tid":1846311,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb38fb1fbd3af9fcf37cdcf4293ffc9040d173b2","tid":1846311,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簽呀"},{"pid":"a0d86c6ffae675611866088b037ac11fbb1ecd9a","tid":1846311,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"要帶白色絲帶"},{"pid":"7a31fde4169132d86843976d232965f6a0bcdf68","tid":1846311,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我支持醫護罷工，逼令政府回應封關訴求</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c9156563bf1fef3f2ab4ac71ab9ad8301d53c2b0","tid":1846311,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即使服務有可能受阻，我或會受到影響，我仍然支持醫護罷工。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5ccb7f9aa205e6dccbe52e470172d5e7ad24f3b6","tid":1846311,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"支持醫護一齊罷工"},{"pid":"b5ad7a84a660d04d9c8ec61d015ef89b60d19a0f","tid":1846311,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"大家簽左未？未簽就快啦！"},{"pid":"0434eafa5488acc3819ee34ac48582c4efdb222e","tid":1846311,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"【twitter戰線】美國及英國議員要求英國政府禁用華為建5G<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Task2 要人，大量議員插華為tweet無人推</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5j2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=268be655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7a31fde4169132d86843976d232965f6a0bcdf68","tid":1846311,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我支持醫護罷工，逼令政府回應封關訴求</span></strong>"}}